        "text": "Eat, Drink and Fight Cancer! Feb 6, 2018 Save \nPlease join Carolynn and Jesus Navarro for a special event dinner on Tuesday, February 20th and support their efforts to raise money for The Leukemia & Lymphoma Society (LLS) and to help patients who are battling blood cancers. \nSimply dine-in or take-out at The Cloverleaf Tavern on Tuesday, February 20th between 5:00 pm–9:00 pm with your friends and family. The Cloverleaf Tavern will donate a percentage of your total dinner check directly to LLS. \nNo reservations necessary. \nUpon arriving, calling-in, and on your receipt please inform the hostess/server that you are supporting the LLS fundraiser. \nIt’s that Simple — Eat, Drink and Fight Cancer! \nCarolynn and Jesus are training to participate in the Novo Nordisk New Jersey Marathon/NJ Long Branch Half Marathon weekend as members of The Leukemia & Lymphoma Society’s (LLS) Team in Training on April 29, 2018. \nWhen: Tuesday, February 20th, 2018 \nWhere: The Cloverleaf Tavern, Caldwell, NJ 07006 (973) 226-9812 \nIf you cannot attend, but would like to make a donation:",
